 "height": 0, "width": 0}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s240x240/recipe674-cook-step2-635520061589237578.jpg", "height": 240, "width": 240}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s480x480/recipe674-cook-step2-635520061589237578.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 480}, {"url": "cong-thuc-ba-ba-nau-chuoi-67495021.jpg", "height": 640, "width": 640}]]}, {"content": "C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m ba ba n\u1ea5u chu\u1ed1i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc b\u1eaft m\u1eaft h\u01a1n: G\u1ecdt v\u1ecf chu\u1ed1i xanh, th\u00e1i mi\u1ebfng m\u1ecfng, ng\u00e2m n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 pha ch\u00fat gi\u1ea5m cho tr\u1eafng.", "photos": [[{"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s/recipe674-prepare-step1-635520050706249297.jpg", "height": 0, "width": 0}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s240x240/recipe674-prepare-step1-635520050706249297.jpg", "height": 240, "width": 240}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s480x480/recipe674-prepare-step1-635520050706249297.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 480}, {"url": "cong-thuc-ba-ba-nau-chuoi-67416706.jpg", "height": 640, "width": 640}]]}, {"content": "\u0110\u1eadu ph\u1ee5 r\u00e1n v\u00e0ng, th\u1ecbt ba ba ch\u1ea7n qua n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00f4i, v\u1edbt ra \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc.", "photos": [[{"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s/recipe674-prepare-step2-635520051556600860.jpg", "height": 0, "width": 0}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s240x240/recipe674-prepare-step2-635520051556600860.jpg", "height": 240, "width": 240}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s480x480/recipe674-prepare-step2-635520051556600860.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 480}, {"url": "cong-thuc-ba-ba-nau-chuoi-67447997.jpg", "height": 640, "width": 640}]]}, {"content": "C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m ba ba n\u1ea5u chu\u1ed1i: Phi th\u01a1m h\u00e0nh, t\u1ecfi, \u0111\u1ebfn khi h\u01a1i v\u00e0ng c\u00f3 m\u00f9i th\u01a1m th\u00ec cho ba ba v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec1u, d\u00f9ng \u0111\u0169a tr\u1ed9n th\u1ecbt l\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1edbi nhau, khi ch\u00edn v\u1eeba t\u01a1i th\u00ec nh\u1ea5c kh\u1ecfi b\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ec3 qua m\u1ed9t b\u00ean.", "photos": [[{"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s/recipe674-prepare-step3-635520056548710235.jpg", "height": 0, "width": 0}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s240x240/recipe674-prepare-step3-635520056548710235.jpg", "height": 240, "width": 240}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s480x480/recipe674-prepare-step3-635520056548710235.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 480}, {"url": "cong-thuc-ba-ba-nau-chuoi-67472828.jpg", "height": 640, "width": 640}], [{"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s/recipe674-prepare-step3-635520056567460235.jpg", "height": 0, "width": 0}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s240x240/recipe674-prepare-step3-635520056567460235.jpg", "height": 240, "width": 240}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s480x480/recipe674-prepare-step3-635520056567460235.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 480}, {"url": "cong-thuc-ba-ba-nau-chuoi-67439090.jpg", "height": 640, "width": 640}]]}, {"content": "Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c phi th\u01a1m h\u00e0nh, t\u1ecfi th\u00eam l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o ch\u1ea3o kh\u00e1c cho chu\u1ed1i xanh v\u00e0o x\u00e0o. Khi chu\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00edn t\u1edbi, cho ba ba v\u00e0o x\u00e0o c\u00f9ng, n\u00eam mu\u1ed1i, b\u1ed9t ng\u1ecdt, ti\u00eau v\u1eeba \u0103n. \u0110\u1ed5 n\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00f9ng v\u00e0o r\u1ed3i n\u1ea5u v\u1edbi l\u1eeda nh\u1ecf. Khi th\u1ecbt ba ba n\u1ea5u chu\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00edn m\u1ec1m, cho \u0111\u1eadu ph\u1ee5 v\u00e0o. \u0110un ba ba n\u1ea5u chu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1eadu ti\u1ebfp kho\u1ea3ng 3 ph\u00fat l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.", "photos": [[{"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s/recipe674-prepare-step4-635520055776522735.jpg", "height": 0, "width": 0}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s240x240/recipe674-prepare-step4-635520055776522735.jpg", "height": 240, "width": 240}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s480x480/recipe674-prepare-step4-635520055776522735.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 480}, {"url": "cong-thuc-ba-ba-nau-chuoi-67429578.jpg", "height": 640, "width": 640}]]}, {"content": "Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eafc ra cho th\u00eam h\u00e0nh, t\u00eda t\u00f4, ti\u00eau th\u00e1i nh\u1ecf v\u00e0o t\u00f4 ba ba n\u1ea5u chu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1eadu. D\u1ecdn ba ba n\u1ea5u chu\u1ed1i n\u00f3ng v\u1edbi b\u00fan ho\u1eb7c c\u01a1m. C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m ba ba n\u1ea5u chu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1eadu n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra m\u00f3n \u0103n th\u01a1m ngon, b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7t cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. L\u01b0u ngay c\u00e1ch n\u1ea5u ba ba om chu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1eadu n\u00e0y ngay, cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e3i c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 nh\u00e9.", "photos": [[{"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s/recipe674-prepare-step5-635520056161991485.JPG", "height": 0, "width": 0}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s240x240/recipe674-prepare-step5-635520056161991485.JPG", "height": 240, "width": 240}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s480x480/recipe674-prepare-step5-635520056161991485.JPG", "height": 480, "width": 480}, {"url": "cong-thuc-ba-ba-nau-chuoi-67459619.JPG", "height": 640, "width": 640}], [{"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s/recipe674-prepare-step5-635520056202772735.jpg", "height": 0, "width": 0}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s240x240/recipe674-prepare-step5-635520056202772735.jpg", "height": 240, "width": 240}, {"url": "https://image.cooky.vn/recipe/g1/674/s480x480/recipe674-prepare-step5-635520056202772735.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 480}, {"url": "cong-thuc-ba-ba-nau-chuoi-67477449.jpg", "height": 640, "width": 640}]]}], "hasCooked": false, "totalCook": 1, "totalLike": 17, "createdOn": 0, "totalTime": 70, "creator": {"totalFollower": 1084, "totalRecipe": 524, "id": 9, "photos": [{"url": "http